{"type":"text","timestamp":1775851897297,"sessionID":"ses_286fb3a50ffevXBFaIE185eANl","part":{"id":"prt_d79056448001A2l6WmUvXLMxxr","messageID":"msg_d79053c37001Ji0wF34KthA3KC","sessionID":"ses_286fb3a50ffevXBFaIE185eANl","type":"text","text":"## AR-010 — Router 会话管理 Archive Summary\n\n### Completed (100%)\n\n**All 53 tasks in 10 phases:**\n- Error types & interfaces (7 error types implementing `APIStatus`)\n- Config & constants (Config struct, RSA/JWT constants)\n- Interfaces (`Store`, `Logger`, `SessionManager`, `JWTManagerInterface`)\n- JWTManager (RSA 2048-bit key generation, RS256 signing, 5-minute expiration)\n- SessionManager (`GetSandboxBySession`, `createSandbox`, Workload Manager HTTP client)\n- Middleware (concurrency limit semaphore, logging, recovery)\n- Reverse proxy (`ReverseProxyWrapper` with Director, ModifyResponse, ErrorHandler)\n- Server & handlers (Gin engine, health endpoints, invoke handlers, graceful shutdown)\n- Mock implementations for testing\n- Validation & coverage (all tests passing)\n\n**Files created:** 14 files including `errors.go`, `config.go`, `jwt.go`, `session_manager.go`, `middleware.go`, `reverse_proxy.go`, `server.go`, `doc.go`, and corresponding test files.\n\n### Deferred\n\n**Open Questions (from design.md):**\n1. JWT key persistence mandatory for production (currently allows ephemeral keys)\n2. Per-entry-point configurable proxy timeout (currently hardcoded)\n3. Independent rate-limiting for session creation (vs. concurrent request limit)\n\n**Original \"Out of Scope\" items (deferred to other ARs):**\n- Distributed session cache (Redis-based) — future work\n- Session eviction/cleanup — covered by AR-008 GC","time":{"start":1775851897293,"end":1775851897293}}}
